<h1>言</h1><p class=neha><span style="color:#cc7700;">yán</span><span class=alesi>(yan2)</span> , <span style="color:#000099;">yàn</span><span class=alesi>(yan4)</span> , <span style="color:#cc7700;">yín</span><span class=alesi>(yin2)</span> <span class=lesi>// pronunciations of 言 in Mandarin Pinyin</span></p><h2>Basic information about 言</h2><div class=abo>
